            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThere is no reason to put off your child’s immunization due to a past or future operation. Having a surgery is not a reason to put off vaccination and a recent vaccination is not a reason to put off a surgery. \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EVaccines boost your child’s immune system and protect them from harmful diseases, such as measles, which can cause blindness and even death.\u003C/p\u003E",
