            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt is not recommended to delay the vaccination schedule. Any time you delay a vaccine, you are increasing your child’s vulnerability to severe diseases.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EAvoid risks and make sure to follow your national immunization schedule to protect your child before they are exposed to a life-threatening disease. Bebbo Vaccination Tool will notify you when is the next vaccine due and help you track all recommended vaccines.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "chatbot_subcategory": 596,
