            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ETo date, only the Pfizer vaccine has been authorized by WHO to vaccinate children 5-16 years old. Some countries started  already vaccination of children 5-11 years old. Children particularly those with underlined health conditions, can be vaccinated with this vaccine as per national recommendations. Please consult your local health specialists/paediatrician for the latest updates on this matter. \u003C/p\u003E",
